sentences.english: Do not feed macaques and wild animals.
sentences.chinese: 請勿餵食獼猴及其它野生動物。

sentences.english: The number of wagging dances per minute told the exact distance to the feeding place.
sentences.chinese: 每分鐘擺尾舞的次數表明了到餵食處的精確距離。

sentences.english: Placidly they continued their eating and feeding routine.
sentences.chinese: 然後它們平靜地進食和餵食。

sentences.english: He's a crusty old gentleman who feeds stray dogs and cats.
sentences.chinese: 他是個令人生畏的老紳士，常餵食離羣的狗和貓。

sentences.english: Hang a couple of bird feeders in a tree and set up a bird bath.
sentences.chinese: 你可以在樹上懸掛幾個餵食器或放置一個小鳥浴盆。

sentences.english: All crabs are fed with fresh sardine fish.
sentences.chinese: 所有軟殼蟹均用新鮮沙丁魚餵食。

sentences.english: None of these effects occurred in mice that ate a broth with no added bacteria.
sentences.chinese: 在餵食不添加細菌的肉湯的老鼠中沒有看到這些效果。

sentences.english: And sometimes, if cats are expecting to be fed and the owner isn't obeying, the cat may swat.
sentences.chinese: 有時，如果貓期望餵食但貓奴沒有順從，貓可能亂抓。

sentences.english: The young couple next to me were feeding each other tofu skewers.
sentences.chinese: 我旁邊的一對年輕情侶在相互餵食豆腐串。

sentences.english: Which animal's baby feeds on the mother's milk?
sentences.chinese: 哪種動物的幼兒是以母奶餵食的？

sentences.english: The process of feeding requires manual separation of the heads.
sentences.chinese: 餵食的過程需要人工的將它的兩個頭分開。

sentences.english: Inquiry into the influence of the pine-seed oil upon Lipid peroxidation of mice which are feeded on high fat feedstuff.
sentences.chinese: 探討松籽油對餵食高脂飼料小鼠脂質過氧化的影響。

sentences.english: Severe pancreatitis triggered by high fat diet and alcoholic intemperance;
sentences.chinese: 探討松籽油對餵食高脂飼料小鼠脂質過氧化的影響。

sentences.english: Feed any and all types of fruits and vegetables diced into ?
sentences.chinese: 餵食並將分類的綠色水果和蔬菜的切成小方塊入？

sentences.english: Vistors are not allowed to feed to animals.
sentences.chinese: 參觀者不得給動物投餵食物。

sentences.english: There's a no- feeding sign over there.
sentences.chinese: 那邊有不許餵食的標誌。
